@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ploeua(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(v1)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.09)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v0 / wp.exp(v2 + 0.97)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.78)) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.11 - v2 + 0.88)))
    v2 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.36 * v1 + 0.89) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
